        </para>
        <para>Install nut on spindle. Tighten the nut to 55 to 60 Lbf-ft (75 to 81 Nm).</para>
        <para>Assure that the locking clip is properly located to prevent it working loose
            <hotlnk document="s05016_3.xml" xrefid="f0501605">(Figure 5)
                <xref refid="f0501605"/>
            </hotlnk>
            .
        </para>
        <para>Install side covers
            <hotlnk document="s05016_2.xml" xrefid="f0501604">(Figure 4)
                <xref refid="f0501604"/>
            </hotlnk>
            .
        </para>
        <para>Install front cover
            <hotlnk document="s05016_2.xml" xrefid="f0501602">(Figure 2)
